.\" Generated for SteamUtility.Cli
.TH STEAMUTILITY.CLI 1 "June 2026" "SteamUtility.Cli 5.0.15" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
SteamUtility.Cli \- Cross-platform Steam utility CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B SteamUtility.Cli
\fICOMMAND\fR [\fIOPTION\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
SteamUtility.Cli is a cross-platform command-line utility for Steam operations.
It is used internally by Steam Game Idler but can also be used standalone.
.PP
All commands that require a live Steam session are marked with \fB[LIVE]\fR.
Commands that work without Steam running are marked with \fB[OFFLINE]\fR.
.SH COMMANDS
Discovery (Offline):
.TP
.B detect
Detect Steam installation path.
.TP
.B libraries
List all Steam library folders.
.TP
.B apps
List all installed apps with metadata.
.TP
.B compatdata
Show compatibility data for Proton/Steam Play.
.TP
.B compat-tools
List available compatibility tools (Proton versions).
.TP
.B compat-mapping
Show app-to-compat-tool mapping.
.TP
.B compat-report
Generate compatibility report for all apps.
.TP
.B state-report
Generate Steam client state report.
.PP
Steam-Native (Live - requires running Steam session):
.TP
.B check_ownership \fI<APPID>\fR
Check if current user owns a specific app.
.TP
.B idle \fI<APPID>\fR [\fI--hours N\fR]
Idle a game for specified hours.
.TP
.B get_achievement_data \fI<APPID>\fR [\fI--cache-dir PATH\fR]
Get achievement data for a game.
.TP
.B unlock_achievement \fI<APPID> <ACHIEVEMENT_ID>\fR
Unlock a specific achievement.
.TP
.B lock_achievement \fI<APPID> <ACHIEVEMENT_ID>\fR
Lock a specific achievement.
.TP
.B toggle_achievement \fI<APPID> <ACHIEVEMENT_ID>\fR
Toggle an achievement.
.TP
.B update_stats \fI<APPID> <STAT_NAME> <VALUE>\fR
Update a statistic value.
.TP
.B reset_all_stats \fI<APPID>\fR
Reset all statistics for a game.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format (for machine parsing).
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Show help for a specific command.
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Show version information.
.SH FILES
.TP
\fI~/.steam/steam/config/loginusers.vdf\fR
Steam user login data (read by detection commands).
.TP
\fI~/.steam/steam/steamapps/\fR
Steam library folders and app manifests.
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.TP
\fBSTEAMUTIL_STEAM_PATH\fR
Override auto-detected Steam installation path.
.TP
\fBSTEAMUTIL_COMPAT_TOOL\fR
Force specific compatibility tool (Proton version).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Detect Steam path:
.B SteamUtility.Cli detect
.TP
List all owned games:
.B SteamUtility.Cli apps
.TP
Idle game for 2 hours:
.B SteamUtility.Cli idle 730 --hours 2
.TP
Get achievement data for CS2:
.B SteamUtility.Cli get_achievement_data 730 --json
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR steam-game-idler (1)
.PP
Full documentation: https://steamgameidler.com/docs
